dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.measurementcalibrationsupport

Interface IMcFunction

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IMcFunction
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IMcFunction: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Represents a functional element to be used as input to support measurement and calibration. It is used to assign calibration parameters to a logical function assign measurement variables to a logical function structure functions hierarchically
